An '''Imperial Intelligence Clearance''' was a document that was issued by [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Imperial Intelligence/Legends|Intelligence]]. Given to those who passed a thorough background check, this certificate granted them access to certain levels of secure information stored in Imperial databases.

